{"type": "article", "id": 12384, "title": "世界上第一台可站可说话的智能书桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125742GFd6AzbgEJR2XfIi.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这台桌子号称是世界上第一台可以站立可以说话的智能书桌。它可以根据用户使用的姿势提供坐式和站立式两种形态，同时，桌面配有智能案板，记忆板，扬声器，USB接口等智能设备，可以像 Siri 一样听从指令而给出反应，也可以配合手机 App，为用户提供更多服务。目前这款桌子正在 Indiegogo 上面众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/ergo-world-s-first-smart-standing-desk-that-talks#/story\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140130G7DtNBd3QLoy5SUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140131aLO4imCqFQhz2j83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65806452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140131MhrP4KvBn2JAyYmN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140132ui0tR1o5SC3WMch7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140132qLgGFVQSNC15Jth0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140132IhJH6ZBogxKmEWqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140133jTDSaiP27QYLwGbv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140133fdIgsBDqPC7VctXm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140134Nj1WOJVE9Yb4tqAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}